{"title":"fix(remediation): correct Deployment selector matchLabels for vigil-app","body":"Root cause: Deployment selector matchLabels (app: vigil-app-typo) does not match template labels (app: vigil-app), causing Kubernetes validation failure during Flux reconciliation.

Evidence: Deployment.apps "vigil-app" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {"app":"vigil-app"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {"matchLabels":{"app":"vigil-app-typo"}}: field is immutable]

Affected resources: Deployment/default/vigil-app, Kustomization/flux-system/cluster-apps"}
